{"primaryContentSections":[{"kind":"declarations","declarations":[{"languages":["occ"],"platforms":["iOS","iPadOS","Mac Catalyst"],"tokens":[{"text":"@property","kind":"keyword"},{"text":" (","kind":"text"},{"text":"nonatomic","kind":"keyword"},{"text":", ","kind":"text"},{"text":"assign","kind":"keyword"},{"text":") ","kind":"text"},{"text":"UIEdgeInsets","preciseIdentifier":"c:@S@UIEdgeInsets","kind":"typeIdentifier"},{"text":" ","kind":"text"},{"text":"contentInset","kind":"identifier"},{"text":";","kind":"text"}]}]},{"kind":"content","content":[{"type":"heading","anchor":"discussion","level":2,"text":"Discussion"},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"When the value of this property is equal to "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"UIEdgeInsetsZero"},{"type":"text","text":", viewport"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"properties such as "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"centerCoordinate"},{"type":"text","text":" assume a viewport that matches the map"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"view’s frame. Otherwise, those properties are inset, excluding part of the"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"frame from the viewport. For instance, if the only the top edge is inset, the"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"map center is effectively shifted downward."}]},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"When the map view’s superview is an instance of "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"UIViewController"},{"type":"text","text":" whose"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"automaticallyAdjustsScrollViewInsets"},{"type":"text","text":" property is "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"YES"},{"type":"text","text":", the value of this"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"property may be overridden at any time."}]},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"The usage of "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"automaticallyAdjustsScrollViewInsets"},{"type":"text","text":" has been deprecated"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"use the map view’s property "},{"type":"reference","identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNMapView\/automaticallyAdjustsContentInset","isActive":true},{"type":"text","text":"instead."}]},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Changing the value of this property updates the map view immediately. If you"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"want to animate the change, use the "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"-setContentInset:animated:completionHandler:"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"method instead."}]}]}],"identifier":{"url":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNMapView\/contentInset","interfaceLanguage":"occ"},"variants":[{"paths":["\/documentation\/maplibre\/mlnmapview\/contentinset"],"traits":[{"interfaceLanguage":"occ"}]}],"kind":"symbol","sections":[],"schemaVersion":{"major":0,"minor":3,"patch":0},"metadata":{"navigatorTitle":[{"text":"contentInset","kind":"identifier"}],"roleHeading":"Instance Property","fragments":[{"text":"contentInset","kind":"identifier"}],"remoteSource":{"url":"https:\/\/github.com\/maplibre\/maplibre-native\/blob\/main\/platform\/ios\/src\/MLNMapView.h#L1610","fileName":"MLNMapView.h"},"title":"contentInset","externalID":"c:objc(cs)MLNMapView(py)contentInset","symbolKind":"property","role":"symbol","modules":[{"name":"MapLibre"}]},"hierarchy":{"paths":[["doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre","doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNMapView"]]},"abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"The distance from the edges of the map view’s frame to the edges of the map"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"view’s logical viewport."}],"references":{"doc://org.swift.MyProject/documentation/MapLibre/MLNMapView/automaticallyAdjustsContentInset":{"type":"topic","abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"A boolean value that indicates if whether the map view should automatically"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"adjust its content insets."}],"identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNMapView\/automaticallyAdjustsContentInset","role":"symbol","title":"automaticallyAdjustsContentInset","kind":"symbol","url":"\/documentation\/maplibre\/mlnmapview\/automaticallyadjustscontentinset","fragments":[{"kind":"identifier","text":"automaticallyAdjustsContentInset"}]},"doc://org.swift.MyProject/documentation/MapLibre/MLNMapView/contentInset":{"type":"topic","identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNMapView\/contentInset","url":"\/documentation\/maplibre\/mlnmapview\/contentinset","kind":"symbol","fragments":[{"text":"contentInset","kind":"identifier"}],"title":"contentInset","role":"symbol","abstract":[{"text":"The distance from the edges of the map view’s frame to the edges of the map","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":"view’s logical viewport."}]},"doc://org.swift.MyProject/documentation/MapLibre":{"kind":"symbol","role":"collection","identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre","title":"MapLibre","url":"\/documentation\/maplibre","abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"Powerful, free and open-source mapping toolkit with full control over data sources and styling."}],"type":"topic"},"doc://org.swift.MyProject/documentation/MapLibre/MLNMapView":{"type":"topic","identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNMapView","url":"\/documentation\/maplibre\/mlnmapview","kind":"symbol","fragments":[{"kind":"identifier","text":"MLNMapView"}],"title":"MLNMapView","role":"symbol","abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"An interactive, customizable map view with an interface similar to the one"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"provided by Apple’s MapKit."}]}}}